scene.message:
Yukino: Yuriko...{nl}
you've... lost! Give it up.{waitkey}{clearbox}Or what? Will you cry and{nl}
cling to your gracious "Snow{nl}
Queen," who gave you{waitkey}"eternal beauty"?{waitkey}{clearbox}What'll it be!! Huh?{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: ...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}{clearbox}You know, Yuriko-chan...{nl}
really...{wait_fr:30} really...{wait_fr:30}{nl}
the Sn-{wait_fr:30}"Snow Queen"...{waitkey}someone like that...{waitkey}I really hate her.{waitkey}{clearbox}You know, Yuriko-chan...{nl}
...this was for the best...{nl}
...{waitkey}{clearbox}Getting to play with{nl}
everyone...{nl}
chat with everyone...{nl}
fight with all my might...{waitkey}and then...{wait_fr:30} getting beaten...{waitkey}{clearbox}Yes...{wait_fr:30} this is how{nl}
it should be...{nl}
...because Yuriko-chan is...{nl}
..."human"{wait_fr:30}, after all...{waitkey}...and "humans"{wait_fr:30} "die"...{waitkey}{clearbox}...Because Yuriko-chan was...{nl}
...a fool...{nl}
...such an obvious thing...{waitkey}...she just couldn't grasp...{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What? You... are you{nl}
crying...?{wait_fr:30} Hmph... how false!{nl}
What are you plotting now?{waitkey}{clearbox}Did you think you could lull{nl}
us off guard with such fake{nl}
tears?{waitkey}{clearbox}There's a limit to making{nl}
fools of people.{waitkey}{clearbox}And to begin with - you, the{nl}
"Snow Queen's" underling, of{nl}
all things to say, that you{waitkey}"really hate" her?{waitkey}{clearbox}If you're going to lie, come{nl}
up with a better lie.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Huh? You're crying?{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan... weak as the{nl}
great me is to a pretty girl's{nl}
tears...{waitkey}{clearbox}I can see right through those{nl}
being fake tears...{waitkey}{clearbox}You're plotting something{nl}
again, but... that won't work.{waitkey}{clearbox}You might fool the others,{nl}
but!{waitkey}{clearbox}You can't trick the eyes of{nl}
the great me. No, really.{waitkey}{clearbox}Besides, you, Miss "Snow{nl}
Queen"-worshipper,{waitkey}{clearbox}saying "Yuriko-chan really{nl}
hates the Snow Queen"?{waitkey}{clearbox}Oh come on... is that a new{nl}
kind of party joke? Lie{nl}
better, Yuriko-chan.{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey...{wait_fr:30} you idiot!{nl}
This girl's really crying!{nl}
Can't you tell by looking?{waitkey}{clearbox}You!! That's why you'll never{nl}
get a girlfriend!{waitkey}{clearbox}You don't understand girls{nl}
at all, like!{waitkey}{clearbox}Mayuzumi too! Don't say such{nl}
harsh things - hear this{nl}
girl out!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hey, Ayase thinks this girl{nl}
isn't such a bad kid...{nl}
...I can't put it{nl}
well, but...{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Thank...{wait_fr:30} you,{nl}
Aya...{wait_fr:30}se? Was it...{waitkey}{clearbox}While I was alive, Yuriko-chan{nl}
wanted to be...{wait_fr:30} your friend...{waitkey}{clearbox}...You know, Yuriko-chan...{nl}
was really...{wait_fr:30} scared.{waitkey}{clearbox}Chatting... playing lots...{waitkey}{clearbox}Lots of boys and friends who{nl}
said they "liked" Yuriko-chan{nl}
...and kind Papa and Mama...{waitkey}{clearbox}Every day was so fun and{nl}
happy...{waitkey}{clearbox}Ahh, I thought, this is my{nl}
"best time"...{waitkey}{clearbox}And then suddenly...{nl}
...I got scared...{waitkey}{clearbox}If now is my "best time,"{nl}
then maybe the rest of my{nl}
life only goes downhill...{waitkey}{clearbox}That's right... Yuriko-chan...{nl}
even if I keep living{nl}
like this{waitkey}{clearbox}I wondered if happiness{nl}
greater than this would{nl}
never, ever come again...{waitkey}{clearbox}Keep living, become an adult,{nl}
...grow old and ugly...{nl}
and just die - when I thought{waitkey}of that,{waitkey}{clearbox}I was scared... so scared...{nl}
I couldn't even sleep{nl}
at night...{waitkey}{clearbox}And then the "Snow Queen"{nl}
mask we used in the play{waitkey}{clearbox}...told Yuriko-chan, "I'll let{nl}
you stay just as you are{nl}
now, forever"...{waitkey}{clearbox}And before I knew it...{nl}
Yuriko-chan was in{nl}
this tower...{waitkey}{clearbox}All alone, all alone...{nl}
forever... in this tower...{waitkey}{clearbox}No Papa, no Mama,{nl}
no friends...{nl}
alone in this tower...{waitkey}{clearbox}Because Yuriko-chan{nl}
was selfish!{waitkey}{clearbox}Because, though I'm human, I{nl}
begged for the impossible -{nl}
"I don't want to die,{waitkey}I don't want to age"...{waitkey}{clearbox}I was a fool! That's why the{nl}
"Snow Queen" deceived me!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Because Yuriko! Because{nl}
Yuriko was a fool!{waitkey}{clearbox}...I was lonely! I wanted it{nl}
to end already! Yuriko-chan{nl}
just couldn't take{nl}
it anymore!!{waitkey}{clearbox}So when you all came...{nl}
...Yuriko...{wait_fr:30} was happy!{waitkey}{clearbox}It could end, by any means...{nl}
I didn't want to be alone{nl}
anymore! So!{wait_fr:30} So!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Hmph...{wait_fr:30} I see.{waitkey}{clearbox}So that terrifying combat{nl}
power of yours was born from{nl}
your own selfish, willful,{waitkey}spoiled heart.{waitkey}{clearbox}Your boundless sorrow and{wait_fr:30}{nl}
regret{waitkey}{clearbox}grew within absolute solitude{nl}
and a span of time you might{nl}
call "eternal"...{waitkey}changed...{waitkey}{clearbox}and at last became a{nl}
ferocity more endless than{nl}
even your own delusions...{waitkey}so it was.{waitkey}{clearbox}That violent heart became the{nl}
trigger for your erratic{nl}
behavior and your "Thanatos"{waitkey}power-up.{waitkey}{clearbox}What a troublesome thing...!{nl}
Well... still, I can't say{nl}
I don't... understand how{waitkey}you feel.{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: That abnormally immense{nl}
combat power of yours{waitkey}{clearbox}was born from sorrow beyond{nl}
all compare, wasn't it...{waitkey}{clearbox}Despairing solitude... and{nl}
unmanageable sorrow{waitkey}{clearbox}gave rise to a ferocity more{nl}
endless than even your own{nl}
delusions.{waitkey}{clearbox}That sorrow and ferocity{nl}
mingled together,{waitkey}{clearbox}and that heart became...{nl}
your erratic behavior, and{waitkey}{clearbox}the Trigger for the Power-up{nl}
of your own Persona,{nl}
"Thanatos"...{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko, you too were... a{nl}
victim of the "Snow Queen,"{nl}
weren't you...{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: But Yuriko-chan...{nl}
thanks to everyone... can{nl}
finally...{wait_fr:30} end it, it seems...{waitkey}{clearbox}Thank you, everyone...{nl}
Thanks to you all,{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan... can die{nl}
properly... still feeling{nl}
like a "human"{wait_fr:30}...{waitkey}it seems...{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan... ha...{wait_fr:30}s to{nl}
g...{wait_fr:30}o...{wait_fr:30} now...{nl}
Everyone...{wait_fr:30} really...{nl}
thank you.{waitkey}Farewell...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: That "Snow Queen"...{nl}
toying so carelessly with{nl}
human lives! With life itself!{waitkey}{clearbox}Unforgivable!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko...{wait_fr:30} we'll do your{nl}
share too! So rest easy{wait_fr:30}...{nl}
and sleep...{waitkey}{ret}
